text: Ingelinn Lossius-Skeie (born 14 December 1976) is a Norwegian politician for the Progress Party. She served as a deputy representative to the Parliament of Norway from Aust-Agder during the term 2017-2021. She hails from Lillesand. ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:People from Lillesand Category:Deputy members of the Storting Category:Progress Party (Norway) politicians Category:Aust-Agder politicians Category:Norwegian women in politics
